{"tha-ap149:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap149:0.2":"Chattavagga ","tha-ap149:0.3":"Maggadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap149:1.1":"“Uttaritvana nadikam, ","tha-ap149:1.2":"vanam gacchati cakkhuma; ","tha-ap149:1.3":"Tamaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap149:1.4":"siddhattham varalakkhanam. ","tha-ap149:2.1":"Kudala pitakamadaya, ","tha-ap149:2.2":"samam katvana tam patham; ","tha-ap149:2.3":"Sattharam abhivadetva, ","tha-ap149:2.4":"sakam cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap149:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap149:3.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap149:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap149:3.4":"maggadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap149:4.1":"Sattapannasakappamhi, ","tha-ap149:4.2":"eko asim janadhipo; ","tha-ap149:4.3":"Namena suppabuddhoti, ","tha-ap149:4.4":"nayako so narissaro. ","tha-ap149:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap149:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap149:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap149:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma maggadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap149:7.1":"Maggadayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}